reviewText:
Early Access Review

Right now, Warbit is a Multiplayer Online FPS that lacks much of content in the moment. There are only three Arenas and much of the options or other things are missing. But what is there is not to bad. The stages (maybe from the Unitystore) are small but nice. Handling is ok. The main problem right now, is that there are too less players in the game, the most of the time, i was alone (EDIT: since my review, i go back from time to time and check, if there are players. i found everytime i few. so you can play with others). So, it is hard to recommend. But, it is only a buck…and maybe you have some friends...

This video shows all the things, that are in the game right now. At the end, another player entered the server. Thanks to him, i was not alone for a few minutes.

https://youtu.be/rT7h-OabGDg
